metadata.name: The Infinite Desire
metadata.description:
The Infinite Desire

We’re holding on to an idealized version of ourselves and imprisoned by our idea of perfection. 
As our desire to be better is infinite to count, all of these flaws and failures are the only things we see.
Ease up on ourselves. 
Enough is enough.

2022 | 3614 × 4244 px | mp4 | 20 secs 

Illustration & animation by Wickana
